<h1>Other Engineering Services</h1>

<p>
In addition to our specialized welding, structural, pressure equipment, and transportation engineering services, we provide a broad range of technical consulting and compliance support tailored to the needs of industrial manufacturers, fabricators, inspection organizations, and equipment owners.
Our additional engineering services include:
•	ASME Quality Control Manual Development and Compliance Support in accordance with CSA B51 and provincial regulatory authorities such as ITSM, TSASK, ABSA, and other applicable jurisdictions 
•	Industrial Failure Analysis, Metallurgical Assessment, and Material Selection Consulting to support root cause investigations, performance evaluation, and optimized material selection for demanding service conditions 
•	ISO 3834 Implementation and Compliance Support for welding quality management systems, process control, and certification readiness 
•	Custom Equipment Fabrication and Modification Design including engineering support for specialized industrial equipment, structural modifications, and application-specific design solutions 
With practical experience across multiple industrial sectors, we provide engineering solutions focused on safety, compliance, reliability, and operational efficiency—helping clients address unique technical challenges with confidence.
</p>

